Special:
  Resistance: 10/- Cold Resistance
  Lesser Circle of Warmth: All other creatures within 10 feet gain 5/- Cold Resistance
Weight: 3 lb.
Required Feat:  Simple Weapon, Mace
Type:  One-handed~
