Special: 
  Spell Process: 15% chance of casting the spell Contagion on target per hit (Fortitude DC 30)
  Venom: +2 points of poison damage every second for 6 seconds (Fortitude DC 24)
  Charisma:  -5 penalty
  Cursed: Can only be removed by a 'Remove Curse' spell
Weight: 5 lb.
Required Feat:  Martial Weapon, Flail
Type:  One-handed~
