@12867    = ~Tower Shield +3~
@12868    = ~This massive shield is nearly as tall as the wielder. Basically, it is a portable wall meant to provide cover. It can provide up to total cover, depending on how far you come out from behind it. A tower shield, however, does not provide cover against targeted spells; a spellcaster can cast a spell on you by targeting the shield you are holding. This shield has runes scribed onto it that glow eerily in dim light.

