@12875    = ~Improved Staff of Power~
@12876    = ~A wizard's staff is far more than just a gilded walking stick, most being enchanted to an impressive degree. This one is no exception, and whoever the previous owner was, they were powerful indeed. It enables a wizard to better escape hostile magic and avoid physical blows, and empowers the wizard's own spells.

STATISTICS:

Damage:  1d6 + 3
Attack Bonus:  +3
Enchantment:  +3
Damage Type:  Bludgeoning
Special:
  Generic Armor Bonus: +3
  Saving Throws: +3
  Spells cast by the wielder gain +3 DC
