@12891    = ~Full Plate Mail~
@12892    = ~Full plate armor is the best armor a warrior can buy, both in appearance and protection. The perfectly fitted interlocking plates are specially angled to deflect arrows and blows, and the entire suit is carefully adorned with rich engraving and embossed detail.

STATISTICS:

Heavy Armor
Armor Bonus: +8
