Special: Can only be removed by a Remove Curse spell~
//@12903    = ~Bone Talisman~
@12904    = ~Bone talismans are highly coveted among practitioners of necromancy.  The charm is created from a piece of bone taken from the remains of a slain vampire.  Usually fashioned into a necklace or ring, the fey magic contained within the talisman enables the wearer to drain the life force from any living creature he or she touches.

