@12907    = ~Potion of Draconic Strength~
@12908    = ~This potion was brewed from the pale yolk found in the white wyrm's egg, combined with some reagents from Imphraili's lab. Though it came at the cost of the future wyrm hatchling's life, the potion grants the strength of a fully grown white wyrm, whose might exceeds that of many giants. This strength lasts for 30 rounds.

